<section>
  <h1>Communication</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>Email</h2>
    <p>
      You will receive the most important information via email sent to the address stored in your
      <%= link_to "profile", :profile, class: "link" %><%= " (in your case #{Current.user.email_address})" if authenticated? %>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>WhatsApp Group</h2>
    <p>
      We have set up a WhatsApp group for questions and last-minute information on the tournament day. However, all
      critical information will be sent via email as described above. So, you won’t miss anything even if you are not
      part of the WhatsApp group. Join the WhatsApp group via
      <%=
        link_to "this link",
          "https://chat.whatsapp.com/DwgJ3hJNPrwDyFWXP3nGBT",
          class: "link",
          target: "_blank",
          rel: "noopener"
      %>
      or scan the QR code below.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <%=
        RQRCode::QRCode
          .new("https://chat.whatsapp.com/DwgJ3hJNPrwDyFWXP3nGBT")
          .as_svg(viewbox: true, fill: :white, color: :black, svg_attributes: {class: "size-48"})
          .html_safe
      %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Further Concerns</h2>
    <p>
      For further concerns that don’t belong in the WhatsApp group, you can always reach out via email to
      <%= mail_to "support@terraforming-cologne.de", class: "link" %>.
    </p>
  </section>
</section>
